{"tid":1801096,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"防暴警上水廣場制服紅衣男     現場市民籲警勿騎頭部","createTime":"2019-12-28T11:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T12:34:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a02c995bc5958f77b318e7a5c5c910b630494e42","tid":1801096,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:22:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499947-20191228.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499947-20191228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNXf7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=b916cf91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499947-20191228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=63bcb8b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499947-20191228.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1499947_1_20191228183130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1499947_1_20191228183130.jpg&h=0371345c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被制服的紅衣男子頭部流血。（馮卓垣攝）<br />\n2019-12-28 HKT 18:31<br />\n<br />\n下午近6時，一批防暴警員突然衝入上水廣場制服一名穿紅色衣服的男子，他掙扎及頭部流血，數名警員將他包圍，並近距離使用胡椒噴劑，再將他按在地上，以索帶綁起雙手。<br />\n<br />\n有在場的市民呼籲警方不要騎在紅衣男子的頭上，警員向市民方向使用胡椒噴劑，在場市民及記者被噴中。<br />\n<br />\n另外，較早時候在上水廣場外天橋位置，一名穿著白衣的男人懷疑拍攝其他人的照片，在場人士打開雨傘包圍他，要求他刪去照片，有人搶走白衣男子的手機，並對他拳打腳踢 。白衣男子之後坐在路邊，有義務急救員協助他，警員表示急救車正在路上。"},{"pid":"a7f8f62de822b75a05d9dc341880aa83d4d4a2fc","tid":1801096,"uid":84949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:23:17.000Z","msg":"need to kill dog directly"},{"pid":"47e839fb729ccb6f0bababd49cae5a347f1dce3c","tid":1801096,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a7f8f62de822b75a05d9dc341880aa83d4d4a2fc","tid":1801096,"uid":84949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:23:17.000Z","msg":"need to kill dog directly"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:30:51.000Z","msg":"其實6月開始已證明咗手無寸鐵係唔WORK"},{"pid":"35a316f7f3c1dc663d9d76cf851545e8e899e64b","tid":1801096,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:31:47.000Z","msg":"東方話紅衫義士企圖搶防暴槍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PqN8.x.HrAJfstbVhG27cA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-12/bbccfda0-2969-11ea-bf6f-50f026d970cc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPqN8.x.HrAJfstbVhG27cA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-12%2Fbbccfda0-2969-11ea-bf6f-50f026d970cc&h=4fb14ff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【18:29】上水廣場內大部分商舖已經落閘，提早結束營業時間。<br />\n<br />\n【18:15】混亂中有示威者圖搶警員的防暴槍，有關示威者已被制服帶走。<br />\n<br />\n【18:00】有一男子疑拍攝黑衣人大頭照被「私了」。防暴警施放胡椒噴霧驅散現場人士。<br />\n<br />\n【17:55】防暴警再次到上水廣場，多次向四周施放胡椒噴劑，有人被警棍打傷。<br />\n<br />\n【17:40】示威者轉而滋擾內地旅客和水貨客。一名男子把一隻疑屬於內地旅客的鞋掟上天橋頂；一名被指是水貨客的女子被搶去購物袋，化妝品和護膚品跌出；多名女士被示威者包圍，其後奔跑至港鐵上水站逃離，其中兩名女子不斷揮動手上毛巾和布，稱自己好驚、好辛苦；有女士手上一袋物品被掟落橋下。"},{"pid":"ad07b34c69c3873b3f69a917d7599531900eacae","tid":1801096,"uid":194560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}